<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset Your Password - <%= appName %>
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>You requested to reset your password. Click the button below to set a new one. This link will expire in 1
            hour.</p>
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>/reset-password?token=<%= token %>" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
        <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= appName %> Team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>